{"tid":1306563,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要]千祈唔好去港交所！ 鄭若驊老公 潘樂陶 嘅公司聽日 (12/7) 就上市！！","createTime":"2019-07-11T07:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T12:52:36.000Z","uid":156968,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3402880aa5f90c848d7483f010d5b3ec001b3838","tid":1306563,"uid":156968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"聽日就喺<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鄭若驊老公</span></strong> 潘樂陶公司 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">ATAL</span></strong> (Code: 1977) 上市嘅大日子！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以千祈唔好去港交所影響佢上市啊！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n為左慶祝，記得將ATAL呢間公司嘅背景分享俾多啲身邊嘅人，特別喺有投資嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>同大家重溫一下呢間公司嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">關係網絡</span></strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q4PDhQ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQ4PDhQ4.png&h=662a3693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英文版<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/eSeNt6V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FeSeNt6V.jpg&h=76f26547&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n當然唔會少得背後嘅兩位<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大戶</span></strong> (i.e. 基石投資者) ，余錦基先生同埋黃森捷先生<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><em>基石投資者（Corner Stone Investor）是指在大規模股份首次發行中，以禁售期換取優先認股權的投資者，多為企業、機構及知名富商，如大型保險機構、大型國有企業和資產管理公司等。</em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢兩個都喺<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">合股供股</span></strong>高手，亦姐喺玩弄<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">財技嘅高手</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><em><strong><em>合股</em></strong><br />\n<em>當股價變得低殘：合股  當莊家重複派貨和印股票的行為之後，股價會變得很低，可能是「仙股」，而港交所的規定中股票的定價下限是0.01元。  <br />\n<br />\n當「炒無可炒」的時候，莊家就可合股，假設把股票10合1，股價便會從0.01元變成0.1元，這個方法透過縮減股票數量令股價突然上升至一個高位，再次製造股價下跌空間，省時省成本之餘，亦方便重施故技。</em></blockquote></em><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><em><strong><em>供股</em></strong><br />\n當股權變得分散：供股  當莊家不斷在市場上沽售，而整個行動又令其股權分散，手握的大權各散東西。  <br />\n<br />\n這個時候，莊家可以1供11等大比例供股，目的除了產生碎股增加供股成本，亦務求讓小股東放棄供股來重掌股權，散戶卻因此面臨兩難。</em></blockquote>[/i]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下喺佢地過往標榜嘅戰績<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IRDvI09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIRDvI09.png&h=924dddcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6MfJn3w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6MfJn3w.png&h=c3a0c19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投資涉及風險，希望大家可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>將賀圖分享去Fb 及各大社交平台</strong></span>，等更多投資者知道，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>投資喺真係有風險</strong></span>，同埋記得<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>投資前要做好功課</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/A00SAnI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FA00SAnI.png&h=1a2b7e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MmxxKEO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMmxxKEO.png&h=3c43f4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q6EEVSA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq6EEVSA.png&h=225bbbd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource<br />\n<blockquote><strong>向攬炒巴團隊致敬</strong><span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1289522\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1289522</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>以上資訊全部均為公開資料整合</strong>"},{"pid":"919cc02cfed9d0df2aa229c99cd72872f46f9481","tid":1306563,"uid":156968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:52:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95b935dcbbfa2cfd9354d1ee43be2dfeef8c04c9","tid":1306563,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"626a1cb41020a427ac3ce92ceadbad7f78801735","tid":1306563,"uid":156968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmo